      "content": "i get that but calling it life-threatening seems kinda intense for a plant, right? i've heard from a few people that a little bit of it is fine. if i just slowly lower my dose of sertraline over a few weeks while i start the st johns wort at the same time, would that make it safer? i really just want to get off the pharmacy stuff.",
